	(3056,222,'content_panels_0_ihp_introduction_paragraph','At Church Barn we develop exceptional residential and commercial schemes, we maintain a diverse investment portfolio, and we work with land owners on strategic promotion.'),
	(3057,222,'_content_panels_0_ihp_introduction_paragraph','field_628ce7bf7d0ed'),
	(3058,222,'content_panels_0_ihp_strapline','Our vision is for high quality design, professionally realised. Thats true whether were refurbishing a single property, delivering a 60,000 sq ft business space, or securing planning permission and plc disposal on a 150 unit residential scheme.  \r\n\r\nInteresting additions to our growing investment portfolio are always welcome. We think laterally when investing, and are happy to evolve our portfolio with the right opportunities. \r\n\r\nWe know how to make the most of land and large property opportunities. Our strategic land promotion offers creative and collaborative solutions that deliver exciting projects and returns.\r\n'),
