	(3082,222,'content_panels_1_primary_content','Church Barn Group is a privately owned and funded property development company, bringing a personal approach to development, investment and land promotion.\r\n\r\nFrom our base in a beautifully refurbished barn on the South Downs Way, we live and breathe development opportunities and work to bring exceptional design to residential and commercial property schemes.\r\n\r\nWith private cash reserves in place, we are primed for fast decisions and immediate investment.'),
