	(3096,222,'content_panels_1_middle_content','Mike Jones has unrivalled knowledge of the South East property market and the sharpest eye for a deal on the South Coast. He founded Church Barn Group after selling the business he built into the areas leading independent estate agency from scratch to Lloyds Development Finance in 2021. \r\n\r\nWith over thirty years experience, Mike specialises in the planning, finance and delivery of residential and commercial schemes. Away from work, an inability to turn down a challenge has landed Mike on the slopes of Everest and seen him marathon running in the South of France, although he usually makes the most of life in a slightly less adventurous manner, sailing, biking, or strolling the South Downs with dogs in tow.'),
